p://backinbeirut.blogspot.com/";s:11:"blog_author";s:13:"Paul Cochrane";s:28:"blog_author_twitter_username";N;s:13:"blog_rss_feed";s:52:"http://backinbeirut.blogspot.com/feeds/posts/default";s:9:"blog_tags";s:14:"tech, business";s:2:"id";i:9;s:11:"blog_active";i:1;s:24:"blog_last_post_timestamp";i:1399376460;}i:18;O:8:"stdClass":26:{s:7:"post_id";i:28723;s:8:"post_url";s:97:"http://www.absolutegeeks.com/2014/04/yougotagift-com-the-middle-easts-online-mall-for-gift-cards/";s:10:"post_title";s:63:"YouGotaGift.com: The Middle East’s Online Mall for Gift Cards";s:10:"post_image";s:94:"http://www.absolutegeeks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Screen-Shot-2014-04-30-at-10.00.57.png";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:123:"YouGotaGift.com is an Online Mall for Gift Cards in the Middle East founded by Abed Bibi and Husain Makiya. The ser...";s:7:"blog_id";s:13:"absolutegeeks";s:14:"post_timestamp";i:1398838800;s:12:"post_content";s:3072:"<p><a href="http://yougotagift.com/">YouGotaGift.com</a> is an Online Mall for Gift Cards in the Middle East founded by Abed Bibi and Husain Makiya. The service offers a great solution and extremely convenient way of sending prepaid gift cards from leading brands using the web and mobile devices.</p>
<p>The eGift Cards can be personalized and instantly delivered by email, Facebook, SMS or simply printed and hand delivered.</p>
<blockquote><p>“According to a research we did in the UAE, fifty percent of people don’t like the gifts [they receive] sometimes, they put it on the shelf and not use it…or plan on exchanging it but never do,” Bibi said.</p></blockquote>
<p>YouGotaGift is currently dealing with retailers in the UAE and has recently entered the Lebanese market. The company is also expanding to other countries in the region.</p>
<blockquote><p>“When you go to visit a married couple for example you don’t know what the lady might like for her home… so I’ll send you this gift card and she’ll go and shop wherever she wants,” Bibi added.</p></blockquote>
<p>In the UAE, <a href="http://yougotagift.com/">YouGotaGift.com</a> have partnered with 55+ leading stores like Virgin Megastore, Galeries Lafayette, S*UCE Gifts, Boutique 1, Faces, iStyle, Vox Cinemas, Ski Dubai, Toys R’ Us and more.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.absolutegeeks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Screen-Shot-2014-04-30-at-10.00.57.png" rel="lightbox-0"><img src="http://www.absolutegeeks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Screen-Shot-2014-04-30-at-10.00.57.png" alt="" width="800" height="366"></a></p>
<h3></h3>
<h2>How does it all work?</h2>
<blockquote><p>“Just pick up a brand from the site… personalize the card, attach a picture, write a message, pick up the amount [of the gift’s worth], then you can send it by SMS, email, Facebook or print it and take it with you to the event,” Bibi explained.</p></blockquote>
<p>YouGotaGift offers wedding registries, corporate gifts and allows people to pitch in for group gifts.</p>
<p><strong>Group Gifts:</strong> Invite a group of friends to contribute for a bigger & better gift that your friend will really like for occasions like birthdays, baby showers, farewells.</p>
<p><strong>Corporate Gifts:</strong> Aimed at rewarding employees and customers online.</p>
<p><strong>Weddings: </strong>Create a money registry and receive the contributed funds in the form of a single LOADnSHOP Prepaid Visa Gift Card. This Gift Card can be used worldwide to shop where Visa is accepted.</p>
<h3></h3>
<h2>AbsoluteGeeks & YouGotaGift</h2>
<p>At AbsoluteGeeks.com we love our readers, so we’ve teamed up with YouGotaGift.com to offer you an AED 30 discount promo voucher. All you need to do is click on <a href="https://yougotagift.com/ref/blogger/ABSGEEKS/ABSOLUTEGEEKS/">this link</a> and you’ll  be automatically eligible for the discount*.</p>
<p>*The offer is valid until May 29, 2014 and can be used on any of the eGift Cards.</p>
<p>Enjoy!</p>
